There is established within the state treasury the early learning trust fund, to be administered by the early learning council, into which shall be deposited all moneys received by the council in the form of:
     (1)  Fees;
     (2)  Grants;
     (3)  Donations;
     (4)  Appropriations made by the legislature to the fund; and
     (5)  Revenues regardless of their source,
and earnings on moneys in the fund.  Moneys in the fund shall be used for the early learning system.  Expenditures from the fund may be made by the council without appropriation or allotment. [L Sp 2008, c 14, pt of §2; am L 2009, c 194, §4]
